      "label": "Condition",
      "value": "The papyrus has been cut off straight on all four sides, causing a loss at the top and bottom sides of several lines. On the left side one word has also been partially cut off. On the left half of the papyrus from lines two to six two or three letters are missing due to a large lacuna. In several other places the papyrus fibres have come off. The letter is continued on the verso in the same handwriting by flipping it over top to bottom."
