    {
      "label": "Content description",
      "value": "The sender writes the addressee that he will buy (or sell) the dates which are with the sender. . He mentions the transportation of goods (weighing seven q\u012br\u0101\u1e6d minus one \u1e25abba five q\u012br\u0101\u1e6d and half a d\u012bn\u0101r). The sender asks the addressee to answer his letter \"the moment he has read it\" (verso ll. 2-3)."
    },
